Welcome to Week 2 of onboarding to our unified work order system and surrounding technologies. This second week will cover the remainder processes in the work order system along with some jobs in the old architecture that this group will continue to use until we have migrated all processes into the new architecture work order system - an effort we are trying to close by the end of 2022.

  • Pre-Processed Data
  • Image Sweeps
  • Relativity Productions
  • HS Requests
  • SD/ETS Tasks
  • Archive and Purge Requests
  • Queue Management
  • Quality Incidents and Tracking
  • Timekeeping
  • InSite Reporting

Please keep in mind that these courses will be supplemented with hands-on training sessions in the coming weeks. If you have any questions, feel free to jot them down and raise during the Q&A sessions, with your SEA/NY aligned pod, and/or supporting BizOps and TS&E resources.

CUO | Client Services Phase 2 - Week 1

 

Welcome to Week 1 of onboarding to our unified work order system and surrounding technologies. This first week will cover an onboarding introduction, an overview of the end-to-end workflow, and the beginnings of the work order system:

  • Onboarding Intro
  • End-to-End Internal Workflow
  • Matter Initiation
  • Data Receipts, Intake, and Advanced Malware Security Scan
  • Core Processing
  • Major Exceptions Processing
  • Decryption Processing
  • ChatSmart Processing
  • Search Term Normalization (STN) and Filter
  • Review
  • Analytics

Please keep in mind that these courses will be supplemented with hands-on training sessions in the coming weeks. If you have any questions, feel free to jot them down and raise during the Q&A sessions, with your SEA/NY aligned pod, and/or supporting BizOps and TS&E resources.
